08:15.620 --> 08:17.655
[ Telephone rings ]

08:20.586 --> 08:23.344
Denver Archdiocese.
The Lord be with you.

08:23.448 --> 08:25.724
And with your spirit,
m'kay.

08:25.827 --> 08:27.689
Uh, my name
is counselor Mackey,

08:27.793 --> 08:29.620
and w-we seem to be having
a little problem

08:29.724 --> 08:31.896
with our local church
here in South Park.

08:32.000 --> 08:34.517
Our, uh -- our priest
has gone missing.

08:34.620 --> 08:36.551
Oh, not another one!

08:36.655 --> 08:38.517
All right.
Listen to me carefully.

08:38.620 --> 08:41.551
Your local priest
has not done anything wrong.

08:41.655 --> 08:43.517
Probably just taking
some time off.

08:43.620 --> 08:45.310
Why is that suspicious?

08:45.413 --> 08:46.724
Well,
it's not suspicious.

08:46.827 --> 08:49.137
We just kind of don't know
what to do, you know?

08:49.241 --> 08:50.344
We'll take care of it.

08:50.448 --> 08:51.862
There's no need
to involve the authorities.

08:51.965 --> 08:54.103
Just sit tight.

08:54.206 --> 08:55.172
[ Button clicks ]

08:55.275 --> 08:57.862
Send in a clean-up crew now.

08:57.965 --> 08:59.482
[ Doors open ]

08:59.586 --> 09:02.103
We've got another one.

09:02.206 --> 09:04.551
A priest in South Park
has gone rogue

09:04.655 --> 09:06.827
and is probably out
doing his thing.

09:06.931 --> 09:10.206
I need you guys to get up there
and clean up his mess.

09:10.310 --> 09:11.793
Don't worry,
Your Holiness.

09:11.896 --> 09:13.517
By the time we're done
with that town,

09:13.620 --> 09:15.379
there won't be a lick of cum
anywhere.

09:15.482 --> 09:18.103
[ Dramatic music plays ]

09:20.000 --> 09:23.551
[ Song playing ]

09:23.655 --> 09:27.482
