09:27.586 --> 09:28.896
Butters:
Happy Birthday, Clyde!

09:29.000 --> 09:31.689
Hope you don't mind
I brought a friend!

09:31.793 --> 09:35.275
For we are God's handiwork,
created in Christ Jesus

09:35.379 --> 09:37.275
to do good works.

09:37.379 --> 09:39.448
Dude, what are you
talking about?

09:39.551 --> 09:40.517
Come on, Father!

09:40.620 --> 09:42.517
Let's go tear up
the skating rink!

09:42.620 --> 09:44.724
Just leave it alone,
Clyde.

09:44.827 --> 09:46.068
Butters brings him
everywhere.

09:46.172 --> 09:47.413
I don't care.

09:47.517 --> 09:49.413
I don't want a priest
at my fucking birthday party!

09:49.517 --> 09:50.931
It's all right, Clyde.
It's all right.

09:51.034 --> 09:53.689
[ Song playing ]

09:53.793 --> 09:56.068
♪♪

09:56.172 --> 09:57.413
That's it!
You're doin' great!

09:57.517 --> 09:59.000
Oh, aah!

09:59.103 --> 10:00.724
Oh, Mother Mary.

10:00.827 --> 10:02.689
I feel like everyone's
staring at me.

10:02.793 --> 10:05.137
[ Children shouting playfully ]

10:05.241 --> 10:06.206
Nobody's staring!

10:06.310 --> 10:07.793
I'm gonna go get us
some soda pop.

10:07.896 --> 10:09.724
You just mingle
with the other fellas!

10:09.827 --> 10:13.206
[ Depressing Country song
playing ]

10:13.310 --> 10:15.551
♪♪

10:15.655 --> 10:18.000
What's it all about, huh?

10:18.103 --> 10:20.137
Are we just bags
of carbon and water

10:20.241 --> 10:22.172
put on this planet
for no purpose?

10:22.275 --> 10:23.896
You're born.

10:24.000 --> 10:25.379
You die.

10:25.482 --> 10:28.137
Then you're just
food for the worms.

10:28.241 --> 10:31.551
It all does seem
pretty meaningless.

10:31.655 --> 10:33.310
Hey!
The church is back open!

10:33.413 --> 10:34.758
There's people inside!

10:34.862 --> 10:36.620
-What?
-They church is back open?

10:36.724 --> 10:37.931
Oh, boy! Let's go!
Let's go!

10:38.034 --> 10:40.655
-The church is back open!
-Thank God! Let's go!

10:40.758 --> 10:42.689
[ Vacuum whirring ]

10:42.793 --> 10:44.551
Scrub everything.

10:44.655 --> 10:45.689
Police can detect

10:45.793 --> 10:47.482
even a milligram of cum
and rectal blood.

10:47.586 --> 10:48.931
Hey!

10:49.034 --> 10:50.551
Oh.
Uh, hello, my children.

10:50.655 --> 10:51.689
The Lord be with you.

10:51.793 --> 10:53.620
Townspeople:
And with your spirit.

10:53.724 --> 10:55.034
What, uh, what are
you guys doing?

10:55.137 --> 10:57.103
Oh, we're just giving the place
a nice scrub down

10:57.206 --> 10:58.862
while we wait
for your priest to come back.

10:58.965 --> 11:00.862
He was called
to South America last week.

11:00.965 --> 11:02.310
Last week?

11:02.413 --> 11:04.379
No, he was at my house
a couple days ago

11:04.482 --> 11:06.000
playing board games
with the boys.

11:06.103 --> 11:07.137
[ Whirring stops ]

11:07.241 --> 11:08.689
No, he wasn't.

11:08.793 --> 11:10.241
Look.
I assure you everything is fine.

11:10.344 --> 11:13.034
Your priest will be back.
Just have some patience.

11:13.137 --> 11:14.379
All: Aw!

11:14.482 --> 11:16.103
Come on,
guys.

11:16.206 --> 11:17.586
[ Vacuum whirs ]

11:17.689 --> 11:18.620
Scrub everything.

11:18.724 --> 11:20.448
Bleach those
board-game pieces.

11:20.551 --> 11:22.344
You find something
on that chair?

11:22.448 --> 11:24.620
It's either blood and cum
or ketchup and mayo.

11:24.724 --> 11:26.000
Well,
just get rid of it.

11:26.103 --> 11:27.620
Bleach the entire
top of the table.

11:27.724 --> 11:30.344
That's probably
where he mounted them.

11:30.448 --> 11:32.482
Uh, excuse me?

11:32.586 --> 11:34.689
Oh. Hello, my son.

11:34.793 --> 11:36.034
What are you doing?

11:36.137 --> 11:37.655
What are we doing
about what?

11:37.758 --> 11:39.000
Well, I mean,
it looks like

11:39.103 --> 11:40.931
you're scrubbing and bleaching
our table and chairs.

11:41.034 --> 11:43.103
Mnh-mnh.
That's not what's going on.

11:43.206 --> 11:45.620
Your local priest was
never here, actually.

11:45.724 --> 11:47.310
Yeah, he was.
I played with him.

11:47.413 --> 11:49.724
Oh, you did?

11:49.827 --> 11:51.620
Better get the Kumby.

11:51.724 --> 11:53.000
What's a Kumby?

11:53.103 --> 11:55.310
We're just here to cleanse
your spirit, my child.

11:55.413 --> 11:56.827
Praise be to Christ.

11:56.931 --> 11:59.758
[ Kumby bloops ]

12:01.551 --> 12:03.448
[ Kumby bloops ]

12:03.551 --> 12:06.827
Boys:
♪ Happy birthday, dear Clyde

12:06.931 --> 12:10.241
