12:10.344 --> 12:11.586
[ Blows out candles ]Boys: Yay!

12:11.689 --> 12:13.517
And now,
let us pray.

12:13.620 --> 12:14.758
Awwww.

12:14.862 --> 12:17.896
Bless us, Oh Lord,
and these thy gifts,

12:18.000 --> 12:19.275
which we are about
to receive...

12:19.379 --> 12:21.758
Kyle, will you do something,
please?

12:21.862 --> 12:22.344
Psalm 78:26 -- He caused the
east wind to blow in the
heavens-

12:22.448 --> 12:22.827
-Why me?

12:22.931 --> 12:23.275
-Kyle!

12:23.379 --> 12:25.000
♪♪

12:25.103 --> 12:27.275
...through Christ,
Our Lord. Amen.

12:27.379 --> 12:30.034
Uh, Butters, can I talk
to you really fast?

12:30.137 --> 12:32.655
Oh, sure, Kyle.
Be right back, Father.

12:32.758 --> 12:34.172
All right, my child.

12:34.275 --> 12:35.344
♪♪

12:35.448 --> 12:36.413
What's up?

12:36.517 --> 12:37.758
Butters, you know,

12:37.862 --> 12:41.310
you can't just bring your priest
with you everywhere.

12:41.413 --> 12:44.310
